BERLINER HANDELS-GESELLSCHAFT v. THE UNITED STATES [No. 42542] [90 C. Cls. 75;

309 U. S. —]

Capital stock excise tax; foreign corporation engaged in business in United States. Decided December 4, 1939; petition dismissed, ante, p. 75.

Petition for writ of certiorari denied by the Supreme •Court March 11, 1940.
